784
00:32:30,279 --> 00:32:32,079
Creo que Shu Han es realmente genial.

785
00:32:32,119 --> 00:32:33,759
De piel clara, hermosa, con piernas largas,

786
00:32:33,799 --> 00:32:35,359
Fresco y generoso.

787
00:32:35,440 --> 00:32:36,559
Podrías considerarla.

788
00:32:36,720 --> 00:32:38,559
